Add website navigation, footer, and several new pages

Integrates new pages (Home, About, Characters, Magic, Hogwarts, Quotes) and UI components (Navigation, Footer). Updates routing in `App.tsx` and `index.html`. Defines API routes for characters, spells, quotes, houses, book parts, and quiz questions in `server/routes.ts`. Updates `server/storage.ts` and `shared/schema.ts` to include new data models for characters, spells, quotes, houses, book parts, and quiz questions. Modifies `tailwind.config.ts` for new font families and `index.css` for scroll behavior.

